2004-11-26
First pre-release for gephex-0.4.2 released
martin

The first pre-release for 0.4.2 is ready for download.
I have built a dist from
gephex@gephex.org--2004/gephex--release--0.4.2--patch-1
.

The sources are located
<a href="http://www.gephex.org/download/src/gephex-0.4.2pre1.tar.bz2">here</a>,
win32 binary release
<a href="http://www.gephex.org/download/win32/gephex-0.4.2pre1.rar">here</a>.

Most important changes since the 0.4.1 release:

<ul>
  <li>support for frei0r plugins</li>

  <li>new modules:
    <ul>	
      <li>centermodule</li>
      <li>pongmodule</li>
    </ul>
  </li>

  <li>updated modules:
    <ul>
      <li>overlay module (new smooth overlay mode thanks to pierre)</li>
      <li>capture module (v4l2 support)</li>
      <li>ifs module (speedup and interface cleanup)</li>
      <li>image output (gl compile fix)</li> 
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

Looking forward to your bug reports (or success stories)!
